by javiereguiluz at 2015-09-07T14:11:34Z

In https://github.com/symfony/symfony/commit/a808fa5c291741de4b5dd9deb9df848704ec3476 I've made some changes for Silex 1 and 2. Let's review the changes:

### Silex 2

**Old toolbar**

![silex_2_before](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/73419/9718212/106c3de4-557a-11e5-9f4f-86eb05bd4744.png)

**New toolbar**

![silex_2_after](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/73419/9718218/16f74cee-557a-11e5-8401-f90963b27531.png)

**New toolbar detail**

![silex_2_after_detail](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/73419/9718229/34126f70-557a-11e5-91b3-d62cc89b8b99.png)

All profiler panels are exactly the same as Symfony, except the following changes:

**Config panel**

![symfony_vs_silex_2_config](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/73419/9718240/5788c6e8-557a-11e5-8c20-ae06f9e78db0.png)

**Logger panel** (there is no channel)

![symfony_vs_silex_2_logger](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/73419/9718245/61e6ed0e-557a-11e5-9f62-db04c1a793c9.png)

**Events panel** (there is no priority)

![symfony_vs_silex_2_events](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/73419/9718248/68e59146-557a-11e5-95fa-5be7206152f6.png)

### Silex 1

First, I cannot make the profiler work for a freshly installed Silex 1 app because of [this issue](https://github.com/silexphp/Silex-WebProfiler/issues/67). The solution is to add the following in `src/app.php`:

```php
$app->register(new Silex\Provider\HttpFragmentServiceProvider());
```

The new toolbar looks the same, but it suffers the same shortcomings of the old toolbar:

1) Instead of "Silex 2", you see the Symfony version:

![silex_1_vs_2_toolbar](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/73419/9718282/bd1ddb60-557a-11e5-9240-d5b9fdfba529.png)

2) The configuration panel also cannot display the Silex version:

![silex_1_vs_2_config](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/73419/9718307/ee04c54a-557a-11e5-896c-50da5cf1d37c.png)

3) The log messages are slightly different:

![silex_1_vs_2_logger](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/73419/9718310/f5dd9d0a-557a-11e5-8807-699bfed02cfb.png)

